  "detailed_description": "<h1>欢迎加入官方交流群</h1><p>灵墟玩家交流QQ1群：534061638（已满）<br>灵墟玩家交流QQ2群：50695950</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>这是一款以仙侠为背景的开放世界单机游戏，在《灵墟》的世界中，你将扮演神秘的“渡魂人遗孤”，在危机四伏的江湖中寻找家门被屠的真相，却因“渡魂人”的身份逐渐陷入更深的谜团当中...扑朔迷离的剧情走向，别具特色的游戏玩法，多种多样的人物生态，丰富新奇的探索谜题，种类繁多的势力技艺，为你呈现出一个身临其境、精彩绝伦、生动庞大的仙侠世界。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※独具特色的世界观与原创剧情设定</h2>上百万字的原创剧情，数十个风格迥异的城镇村落，让你如同身临其境般体验与众不同的江湖故事。在这里，有人和怪物的天人交战；在这里，亦有情比金坚的落难鸳鸯；在这里，亦有血浓于水的骨肉亲情。种类繁多的江湖任务，奇人逸事，等待你在《灵墟》庞大的世界中慢慢发现。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/9c2b5f498715f73e8073ec64983e500d.poster.avif?t=1768376126\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/9c2b5f498715f73e8073ec64983e500d.webm?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/9c2b5f498715f73e8073ec64983e500d.mp4?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※英魂&功法&魂格——创造别具一格的角色成长体系</h2>修行附魂秘术的你，使英魂附魂己身，参与战斗。每位英魂各具特色，自由选择英魂参悟的武学并可搭配多种效果的魂格，通过不同的英魂及武学魂格搭配，让每一场战斗的体验都不尽相同。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/752ed48652aa3551a7cbee042e3b71ae.poster.avif?t=1768376126\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/752ed48652aa3551a7cbee042e3b71ae.webm?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/752ed48652aa3551a7cbee042e3b71ae.mp4?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※众多江湖势力，掌握独门技艺</h2>《灵墟》的世界中遍布各大势力，炼丹、厨艺、寻宝，让你沉浸式体验江湖大侠所能做的任何事情，每一次收获，都能让你的实力更上一层楼。当然，还有钓鱼、采集、种地、捕虫、驯兽、加工制造、收集等多种技艺玩法等待你的发掘。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/e505d6625add9cb48b3e9547f745c712.poster.avif?t=1768376126\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/e505d6625add9cb48b3e9547f745c712.webm?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/e505d6625add9cb48b3e9547f745c712.mp4?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※抽茧剥丝寻找线索，寻找并剿灭灵墟藏匿在人间的首领，维护世界的和平</h2>独特的谜题设计，别致的线索铺设，各具风格的首领机制，不同属性的套装效果，组成了情报首领的特殊玩法。在亦真亦假的线索中抽茧剥丝，找到首领所在，将其剿灭，守护灵武大陆的和平。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/42c848c65221cc947e9839565f202b84.poster.avif?t=1768376126\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/42c848c65221cc947e9839565f202b84.webm?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/42c848c65221cc947e9839565f202b84.mp4?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※种类丰富的江湖奇遇，遍布世界的武修同仁</h2>灵武大陆中有各种各样的奇遇事件、节日活动，还有种类繁多的武修同仁。你的每一个举动或许都能让你巧得机缘一步冲天，当然也有可能让你万劫不复。与武修同仁或结交、或劫杀，影响你在门派中的地位，或许一次小小的劫杀能让你获得门派的不传绝学，当然也可能因为你的不当举动被整个门派世界追杀。掌控自己的命运，通过不断的奋斗，逆天改命，整个世界唯我独尊。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/d555e5f4fd6283aa86aa6df125356bcb.poster.avif?t=1768376126\" width=614 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/d555e5f4fd6283aa86aa6df125356bcb.webm?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1986010/extras/d555e5f4fd6283aa86aa6df125356bcb.mp4?t=1768376126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>除此之外，你还能在游戏中体验到，各具特色的魂观、丰富多样的装备、动态变化的日夜天气、遍布世界的灵纹密藏、作用强大的灵兽仙宠等等。这些，就需要你亲自在《灵墟》的世界中慢慢探寻了......",
